{block content}
<div class="jumbotron">
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Want better newsletters on <span class="img-replace" title="Stack Exchange">Stack Exchange</span> ?</h1>
        <p>StackLetter is a personalized newsletter for the Stack Exchange Network.</p>
        <p class="btn-block"><a class="btn btn-custom btn-xl" href="#signup" role="button">Yes, please!</a></p>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="gray-block">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="overlap">
            <ul class="features pos">
                <li><span class="fa fa-check-circle"></span>Adaptive newsletter sections</li>
                <li><span class="fa fa-check-circle"></span>Personalized content</li>
                <li><span class="fa fa-check-circle"></span>Actual information</li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="features neg">
                <li><span class="fa fa-times-circle"></span>No random content</li>
                <li><span class="fa fa-times-circle"></span>No topic mismatched content</li>
                <li><span class="fa fa-times-circle"></span>No months old content</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <h1 class="sec-title" id="about">What is StackLetter?</h1>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
                <p class="lead text-center">
                    StackLetter is a research project realized at Slovak University of Technology.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 about-stack-letter">
                <h4>What the community thinks about the <a href="https://stackexchange.com/newsletters" target="_blank">current newsletter</a>?</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Newsletter is not <a target="_blank" href="https://meta.stackexchange.com/questions/247298/how-about-an-interesting-newsletter" title="How about an interesting newsletter?">interesting</a> at all!</li>
                    <li>Newsletter is static and not <a target="_blank" href="https://meta.stackexchange.com/questions/110902/can-newsletters-take-into-account-a-users-favorite-tags-on-that-site" title="Can newsletters take into account a user's favorite tags on that site?">personalized</a>? Is this 21th century?</li>
                    <li><a target="_blank" href="https://meta.stackexchange.com/questions/96758/weekly-site-newsletters?rq=1" title="Weekly site newsletters?">Randomly generated content</a> of the newsletter&hellip; Who is&nbsp;interested in&nbsp;randomly generated content?</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 about-stack-letter">
                <h4>What are we going to do?</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Personalized newsletter created <em>only for you</em>!</li>
                    <li>Dynamically <em>adapt newsletter structure</em> dependening on your Stack Exchange activity.</li>
                    <li>Use <em>machine learning</em> and <em>recommender systems</em> for personalization of newsletter content.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="white-block">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="sec-title" id="signup">Sign up for StackLetter</h1>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
                <p class="lead text-center">
                  StackLetter will work as standard StackExchange newsletter. After signing up, you will choose from available StackExchange platforms for sending personalized newsletter.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <ol class="signup-steps">
            <li class="done">Authorize</li>
            <li n:class="isset($presenter->session->registered) ? done">Select sites</li>
            <li n:class="isset($presenter->session->registered) ? done">Done!</li>
        </ol>

        <p class="text-center lead" n:ifset="$presenter->session->registered">
            <br><span class="fa fa-check-circle"></span> You're all done!
        </p>

        <p class="text-center" n:if="!isset($presenter->session->registered)">
            <br><a n:href="authorize!" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary"><span class="fa fa-lock"></span> Authorize StackLetter</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="gray-block">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="sec-title" id="authors">People behind StackLetter</h1>

        <p class="lead text-center">
            StackLetter is a research project of Data Analysis Research Group<br>
            at Faculty of Informatics and Information technology, Slovak University of Technology in Bratislava.
        </p>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4 author">
                <img src="{$basePath}/assets/img/matus.jpg" alt="Matúš Salát">
                <h3>Matúš Salát</h3>
                <p>Master's student at FIIT STU</p>
                <p class="contact">
                    <i class="fa fa-github"></i> <a href="https://github.com/mmatusSVK">mmatusSVK</a><br>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 author">
                <img src="{$basePath}/assets/img/martin.jpg" alt="Martin Šrank">
                <h3>Martin Šrank</h3>
                <p>Master's student at FIIT STU</p>
                <p class="contact">
                    <i class="fa fa-github"></i> <a href="https://github.com/smasty">smasty</a><br>
                    <i class="fa fa-twitter"></i> <a href="https://twitter.com/smasty">smasty</a><br>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 author">
                <img src="{$basePath}/assets/img/ivan.jpg" alt="Ivan Srba">
                <h3>Ivan Srba</h3>
                <p>Supervisor<br>Research fellow at FIIT STU</p>
                <p class="contact">
                    <i class="fa fa-github"></i> <a href="https://github.com/mmatusSVK">isrba</a><br>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 faculty">
                <p class="text-center">
                    <a href="http://www.fiit.stuba.sk/en"><img src="{$basePath}/assets/img/fiit.png" alt="" height="52"></a>
                    <a href="https://www.pewe.sk/datalys"><img src="{$basePath}/assets/img/datalys.png" alt="" height="60"></a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="white-block">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="sec-title" id="contact">Contact us</h1>
        <p class="lead text-center">If you have any questions or concerns, don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-9 col-md-offset-1">
                <form n:name="contactForm" class="form-horizontal contact-form">
                    <div class="alert alert-danger" n:if="$form->hasErrors()">
                        <p n:foreach="$form->errors as $error">{$error}</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label n:name="name" class="col-sm-4 control-label">Name</label>
                        <div class="col-sm-6">
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" n:name="name">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label n:name="mail" class="col-sm-4 control-label">E-mail</label>
                        <div class="col-sm-6">
                            <input type="mail" class="form-control" n:name="mail">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label n:name="body" class="col-sm-4 control-label">Message</label>
                        <div class="col-sm-6">
                            <textarea n:name="body" cols="30" rows="5" class="form-control"></textarea>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group form-group-lg">
                        <label class="col-sm-4 control-label"></label>
                        <div class="col-sm-6">
                            <button n:name="send" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary btn-block">Send</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-right">
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
